How to ACL2s:

-Go to eclipse
-Enter ./eclipse
-Go to Open Perspective in top right corner
-Select ACL2 Development
-Go to File -> New -> Project
-Press next
-Enter project name (eg: Lab1)
-Go to File -> New -> ACL2s/Lisp File
-Drag windows to appropriate places

To Run:

-Go to Advance todo line
-To run again must first Cancel all todo forms

To change session type:

-Go to Stop/kill session
-Go to ACL2s -> Set Session mode